    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors have been formally assessed and meet or exceed required levels for MRL 3. The Use Error factor was not assessed on the basis that the automated scripting pipeline eliminates direct operator interaction during production runs. The assessment team accepted this argument and recorded the factor as not-assessed rather than not-applicable. All validation results demonstrate agreement within acceptance criteria. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device.",
